Grimlock strained to lift himself, his sneer still there. Now he was
pissed off, cause he didnt get to kill "poor" Branded slowly, and eat
his Spark. He transformed, then took one last look down, and fired a
rocket down for good measures, then jumped into the air, heading back up
to the next level.
